{"tid":575762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳 茂 波 經 營 非 法 劏 房","createTime":"2018-02-28T11:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T10:37:19.000Z","uid":47359,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6231b057fb154a35338d8e34fd7419366cdc4d","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"陳茂波經營非法劏房<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n《英治亂局》<br />\n【本報訊】特區政府近年強調要打擊「劏房」，但剛負起此重任的新任發展局長陳茂波卻涉嫌知法犯法。本報發現，陳茂波妻子許步明持有的公司，名下位於佐敦和大角嘴的物業至今仍繼續經營劏房，且涉違反建築物條例。有立法會議員指陳茂波不可能不知情，事件已令其誠信受質疑。<br />\n記者：林偉聰、韓耀庭、張岳弢、吳子葵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波曾任董事的景捷發展有限公司，仍持有大角嘴海興大樓一單位。　黎樹雄攝<br />\n<br />\n本報昨報道，陳茂波94年和95年間，透過任職董事的「景捷發展有限公司」購入多個大角嘴的單位。陳茂波97年辭任該公司董事後，由其妻許步明出任董事及持有股份。本報進一步發現，該公司至今仍持有兩個單位，其中一個位於大角嘴海興大樓4樓A4室。記者昨午到訪上址，發現大門後是一條闊3呎長18呎的走廊，單位內有三間劏房，牆上有三個獨立電錶及水錶，水管分別延伸至三間房內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海興大樓4樓A4單位被一劏三。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劏房面積僅100多平方呎，窗戶面向天井。<br />\n<br />\n一劏五最細單位租逾千元<br />\n<br />\n面積約100多平方呎的3號劏房，住了朱氏三口，內裏有狹小的廚廁，廳放了床和簡單家具後已幾乎無空間走動。房有兩扇窗，窗外是約60平方呎的天井。即將升中四的朱同學說父母上班不在家，一家人租住此單位約一年，月租2,000多元。關掉房燈後房內頓漆黑一片，朱說︰「平時日頭唔開燈就係咁黑。」<br />\n走廊盡頭的1號劏房則有自稱獨居的女住客，她表示透過朋友租住此劏房；2號劏房則傳出成年人及小童叫聲，他們都不願回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佐敦上海街136號4樓被業主一劏五出租。<br />\n<br />\n「做發展局長點有說服力」<br />\n<br />\n記者到景捷仍持有的另一物業上海街136號4樓單位，發現本一梯一伙的單位已變成五個獨立單位，但共用廚房和廁所。一名居於上址逾一年的老伯表示，其單位只有3呎乘9呎，是上址最小的劏房，僅可放一張單人床及一個小櫃，房內無窗，月租1,260元，即呎租達46元。<br />\n測量師學會建築測量組副主席龔瑞麟指，《建築物條例》要求，房間須有一定面積比例向街作採光，窗的面積最小是房間面積的十分一，而十六分一面積的窗戶能打開﹔若窗戶向天井，天井的平面面積最小要21平方米（約226平方呎），再配合垂直高度比例及角度等規限才符合標準。他說︰「除非係超巨型天井，否則相信99%的劏房窗戶向天井都係違規。」<br />\n立法會房屋事務委員會主席李永達直指，事件涉及陳茂波的誠信問題。他解釋，陳曾任該公司董事，就算已辭任，也無可能不清楚妻子持有公司的物業用作經營劏房，「首先劏房一般都違反咗建築物條例，而佢家係做發展局長，負責屋宇署處理所有僭建、建築物條例，佢一定要出嚟交代，唔係對公眾點會有說服力？」陳茂波透過發展局回應表示，需時了解。<br />\n被外界視為特首梁振英金主的恒隆地產董事長陳啟宗，昨力撐陳茂波是出任發展局長的合適人選，並以政務官為例，指香港政府一直由政務官運作，「政務官唔係專才，而係全才，97回歸前已經由政務官去做司長局長，點解當時冇質疑，家就有人質疑先？」他認為只要有能力，就能勝任局長職位。"},{"pid":"b383036fc6c3813606215b84ef144709a7a4f693","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/194051_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F194051_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=527c63f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5332cf1bb75748a5f4e17c56880f72a0e705d5d","tid":575762,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來佢係劏房大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"4c406ca29326c188448d62b2afba0ee4043072d2","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"d5332cf1bb75748a5f4e17c56880f72a0e705d5d","tid":575762,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來佢係劏房大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱出世?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af48a1c444bb447882e8a7e487ca1abd7797b39","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"source蘋果日報"},{"pid":"b593fc49f8a09a9c8ce73bb7a81cbda81458cead","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"2012年發生咋<br />\n大家唔好咁快失憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e2ac384130fd9c8919607bb508abc144f09752","tid":575762,"uid":172893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c406ca29326c188448d62b2afba0ee4043072d2","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"d5332cf1bb75748a5f4e17c56880f72a0e705d5d","tid":575762,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來佢係劏房大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱出世?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"巴打啱啱放監？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有名你叫劏房波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aba43e26136b0fba0cd88e5db76f1bf2d0b637e","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"94e2ac384130fd9c8919607bb508abc144f09752","tid":575762,"uid":172893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c406ca29326c188448d62b2afba0ee4043072d2","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"d5332cf1bb75748a5f4e17c56880f72a0e705d5d","tid":575762,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來佢係劏房大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱出世?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"巴打啱啱放監？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有名你叫劏房波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"重有醉駕波囤地波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c76842f8f09346e4ca3dcc573f5b2f55f54523a","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陳茂波指樓價高企致寢食難安　曾被揭搞劏房囤農地<br />\n</span><br />\n 2017-12-24 14:55字體： A A A<br />\n曾經營「劏房」牟利的財政司司長陳茂波今日在網誌撰文，指樓價高企令自己寢食難安。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指現時樓價高企加重港人負擔，而且窒礙各行各業的發展及青年創業機會，「實在令我寢食難安」。他指現時住屋、辦公室、工業、創意及安老服務等均有空間不足的情況，政府正致力全方面覓地並以多角度探索解決方案。他亦指港府需盡力增加土地供應，希望港人不要以「零和遊戲」的執著心態計較每項土地供應建議，甚至是每幅地的用途。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波現時因樓價高企寢食難安，唯2012年就任發展局局長時，卻被「踢爆」曾經經營劏房牟利。陳茂波在2012年上任發展局局長翌日，被揭在1994至95年間擔任景捷發展有限公司董事期間，曾透過該公司購入多個大角咀單位作「劏房」出租。陳茂波雖指自己毫不知情，但又被踢爆景捷94年購入大角咀一幢大廈單位時，賣合約已寫明單位被「劏開」三間房，可見他當時已知建築違規。陳茂波其後解釋指單位為板間房而不是劏房。另外，新界東北發展計劃爭議期間，陳茂波又被揭發，其家族在新界東北發展區囤地，有利益衝突之嫌。"},{"pid":"33d106755441d28acca954e311060addcfa831e6","tid":575762,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"波波有排起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5756a98dfbfa45c3d09e2617e83940c4d9009c","tid":575762,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5332cf1bb75748a5f4e17c56880f72a0e705d5d","tid":575762,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來佢係劏房大王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"衰十一坐左幾年？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca26df715bf325bb54a4433a02596bcd75b28680","tid":575762,"uid":162539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"當年上埋頭條都官照升錢照賺<br />\n<br />\n你而家咁樣就算俾十萬個正皮你都無用啦<br />\n<br />\n其實根本無人唔記得，係記得又如何？人無耻便無敵"},{"pid":"16027ca539117c094086f4ba312a51aa894c897c","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca26df715bf325bb54a4433a02596bcd75b28680","tid":575762,"uid":162539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"當年上埋頭條都官照升錢照賺<br />\n<br />\n你而家咁樣就算俾十萬個正皮你都無用啦<br />\n<br />\n其實根本無人唔記得，係記得又如何？人無耻便無敵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"咁都冇計架<br />\nforum用途就係咁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6f639f4fc6c5da40634f1bf50d793108c5bc8c","tid":575762,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"活學活用 <br />\n下年推公屋劏房"},{"pid":"6c96d765715b1e90e6ac840e26828cd292d1cfa0","tid":575762,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"係香港要升官就係要有醜聞，有痛腳，咁政府先會用你，因為知道你唯有靠政府先可以生存到，一定會企政府個邊，亦都方便政府控制你"},{"pid":"c3e318c1fcca7759c865628e28d071fa14a672f8","tid":575762,"uid":172893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d92cccb38a00242dc16b498bf24f358c6a9c74","tid":575762,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"做乜唔搞劏房補貼....<br />\n又可以補貼埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1887218b5ccd1f9865884a05e49078b0fc470a7b","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c96d765715b1e90e6ac840e26828cd292d1cfa0","tid":575762,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"係香港要升官就係要有醜聞，有痛腳，咁政府先會用你，因為知道你唯有靠政府先可以生存到，一定會企政府個邊，亦都方便政府控制你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"共產黨一貫做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2364230c1959aa954d0ea42dc6dd0ae92e2e8108","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">接連爆囤地、僭建醜聞致民望低走</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，陳茂波出任發展局局長後的第二天，即被報章揭發他在1994年和1995年間，透過當時任職董事的景捷發展有限公司購入多個大角咀單位作「劏房」出租牟利，涉嫌違反《建築物條例》，被譏為「劏房波」，陳辯稱他買入的單位只有「板間房」而不是「劏房」，引來社會批評。其後，陳又被揭發其妻子許步明旗下的景捷發展，涉嫌與田生集團合謀隱瞞買賣的大角咀一個住宅單位近六成樓價，結果令其少交數十萬元利得稅，被指有避稅之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n除了被指以劏房牟利及涉嫌避稅以外，陳茂波主理的新界東北發展計劃亦掀起極大爭議，最終政府決定按原定計劃拓展新市鎮，其後又被揭發其妻許步明及家人在古洞北發展區擁有最少三幅農地，由陳茂波於1994年以35萬元親自買入，政府收地時估計可坐收1,245萬元賠償，因此他涉嫌在處理新界東北發展計劃時沒有申報利益，社會上不乏要求他下台的聲音，批評他沒有誠信。"},{"pid":"d32898dd7870b9ed1063554081057888b43b869a","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ae534e14dc2ad3f4e3643214c19fa826a9748f","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a32805fa0eb55f0e463c32fe98f372fa9c473d7","tid":575762,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abac5c601ef02ebd6002f946bc2db2ec6cec76cb","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9516deaf2e29897ad1b60d2606c5412332b2b3a","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d7a6422b1762fc6213b9f2dbd509443b6beac8","tid":575762,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}